{"tid":1606334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram 定時求救訊息範本","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T23:21:59.000Z","uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10c047820d32fc03dde7682bb1fadfa75892a2e3","tid":1606334,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"唔知有Telegram定時訊息既睇左呢個先：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1603475/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1603475/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完你會話入面咪寫左要比個人資料囉，仲要乜範本？<br />\n咁你睇左我個版本先：<br />\n<br />\n以下為延遲訊息，作為2019-10-01被捕或其他令我失去聯絡事件的後備手段<br />\n為免因忘記刪除訊息或者其他原因造成誤會，可先嘗試致電個人手機確認<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 加入日期，唔小心早Send左唔會誤會<br />\n2. 加入更多聯絡電話(你塞10個都得，但2個至少啦好無<br />\n3. 安全地點紀錄，最驚連係邊唔見左個人都唔知"},{"pid":"dfb2eb72e175e30a1f689ea24b06e7889982cb6c","tid":1606334,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"包少左頭兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d6c205cd8388867b211085d3fe111468c02796","tid":1606334,"uid":26362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"推定比其他手足見到"},{"pid":"b18b4a357af5e75c79b74411f6d25c3567c01dc1","tid":1606334,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc5ef43315ed77574cd975a6734f1f298d18d9e","tid":1606334,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum